Installation manual:
    * Java 16
    * highly recommended to use: IntelliJ.

To publish your game: (Or follow the official guide by Jetbrains)
    [!] you need to be using IntelliJ follow this guide!
    * Goto File/Project Structure/Artifact
    * press the + and select Jar > From module with dependency
    * Select the Main.java file(Or your main file). Then press Ok

    * double tap Shift and search: "edit configuration"
    * press the + button
    * select Jar Application
    * Then select "Path to JAR" then select the .jar in out/artifacts/NAME_jar(you may have to build before it shows up)
    * And.... TA-DA! you're done with the hard part! Now just build and you're done!
